{"tid":2217350,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"伊院 84 歲男病人死亡　累計 105 死　病人為「慶回歸群組」密切接觸者","createTime":"2020-09-25T11:05:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T15:56:28.000Z","uid":5195,"like":70,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"ae836cefb404175c57728e10bc4d91bb53c5f99e","tid":2217350,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T11:05:29.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情緩和，但再有病人染病去世。醫管局今日（25日）公布，伊利沙伯醫院一名 84 歲有長期病患的男病人（#2007）去世。病人 7 月 21 日因咳嗽及發燒入住伊利沙伯醫院，之後情況持續惡化，延至今日下午 4 時 45 分離世。截至現時，已累計 105 名病人感染武漢肺炎後離世。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料顯示，病人居住慈雲山慈民邨民健樓，與另一名 49 歲女病人（#1774）有關連；而該女病人已經出院，屬於逾 40 人確診的旺角稻香「慶回歸群組」。"},{"pid":"e58c623698a8785a6693560ba087f5fd1cf41b57","tid":2217350,"uid":134474,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T11:06:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eRUdk48.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeRUdk48.gif&h=15e3b8d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54ff8cba4f7931942e53acd1addba7434f36deed","tid":2217350,"uid":123053,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T11:07:50.000Z","msg":"下世再慶過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdf299ec7860d9528e5ae6b77800867407d7e6b9","tid":2217350,"uid":199670,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T11:08:40.000Z","msg":"84歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 早應該死啦認真 香港人口老化嚴重到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73711b27d61f86c2d4f5165d8bec95613b9023c5","tid":2217350,"uid":25794,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T11:08:41.000Z","msg":"用生命慶祝回歸<br />\n幾時追頒個金紫荊俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b26e9a187851113a69252d91d4ce1527d683a9","tid":22